<h1>Youngest director</h1>

<p>The youngest director in our dataset right now is 
<%director_list = Director.where.not({ :dob => nil }).order({ :dob => :desc })%>
<%youngest = director_list.at(0)%>
<a href="/directors/<%=youngest.id%>"><%=youngest.name%></a>, born on <%=youngest.dob%> .</p>

<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>
